  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><span>It is considered uncouth in the news business to reflect on things that happened a few days ago — that is “olds”, not “news”. But we’re making a very conscious attempt to give you early and repeated signal on trends and not just headlines with AINews. To wit, although we already reported on </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/ainews-claude-cowork-dispatch-anthropics\" rel>Claude Cowork Dispatch</a><span>, and Claude Cowork Dispatch Computer Use (a result of last month’s </span><a href=\"https://x.com/AnthropicAI/status/2026705792033026465?s=20\" rel>Vercept acquisition</a><span>) was technically </span><a href=\"https://x.com/claudeai/status/2036195789601374705?s=20\" rel>launched yesterday</a><span>, the reception has been FAR and away Claude’s biggest launch of all time (inclusive of @AnthropicAI):</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!yFgk!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/53ecbdae-6295-4dcf-cd4e-f36f0f50ed00/public 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png\" width=\"1200\" height=\"667.5824175824176\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;large&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:810,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;bytes&quot;:254981,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/192168831?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f225745b-cfdc-41a3-0713-04833c76cc00/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260326040303_6f346c8a-0223-4e5f-adc4-7b5c190beadf_1521x846.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-large\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378